title: Schedule of Judge Sotomayor's Capitol Hill meetings today, 6-10-09 | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House




June 10, 2009

 



Schedule of Judge Sotomayor's Capitol Hill meetings today, 6-10-09




 THE WHITE HOUSE Office of the Press Secretary  ________________________________________________  For Immediate Release                   June 10, 2009    UPDATED SCHEDULE OF JUDGE SOTOMAYOR’S CAPITOL HILL MEETINGS  WEDNESDAY, JUNE 10 South Portico  Today, Judge Sotomayor will visit Capitol Hill to meet with the following Senators: Senator Sherrod Brown  Senator Sam Brownback  Senator Kent Conrad  Senator Russ Feingold  Senator Carl Levin  Senator Joe Lieberman  Senator Blanche Lincoln
